<P>If we <HI>&s;hew our &s;elves men,</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> &s;hall perceive, That there is <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> the <HI>Chri&s;tian Religion,</HI> unworthy <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> GOD. We read in 1 Tim. 3.<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">&punc; <HI>Without Controver&s;y, great is the My&s;te|ry of Godline&s;s.</HI> There are two Thing<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> which render the <HI>Religion</HI> of our Lord
