Salvation</HI> of our Lord Seal'd unto you. <HI>Why</HI> do you maintain the <HI>Eccle&s;iasti|cal Di&s;cipline? <HI>Shew your &s;elves men</HI></HI>; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">et it be, to Recover Fallen Sinners unto <HI>Repentance,</HI> and Repre&s;ent unto the world, what &s;ort of Sinners will be <HI>Ban<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">&s;hed</HI> from the Heavenly Kingdom&punc; Finally, <HI>Why</HI> do you ca&s;t your Mi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">, into the <HI>Lords-dayes Collections? <HI>Shew your &s;elves men</HI></HI>; let it be, to pay your <HI>Quit-rents</HI> unto the Great Lord of all your po&s;&s;e&s;&s;ions; and that the<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e things going up as a <HI>Memorial</HI> before God in Heaven, you may be fitted for His Heavenly Mercies. This is <HI>Ma<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">|ly Religion.</HI></P>
<P N="7">VII. <HI>Shew your &s;elves men,</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> whether God have Di&s;pen&s;ed <HI>Comforts,</HI> or <HI>Sorrows</HI> unto you, Endeavour to <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> the <HI>Calls</HI> of tho&s;e <HI>Di&s;pen&s;ations.</HI> It is the part of a <HI>Rea&s;onable</HI> man, to think, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> may be the <HI>Rea&s;on</HI> &amp; the <HI>De<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">gn</HI> of the Lords Dealings with him, and to com|ply with the Lords <HI>De&s;ign in all.</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> our God multiplied <HI>Comforts</HI> unto us? We do not <HI>&s;hew our &s;elves</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> we
